## English Summary

This project uses a **Research & Collaboration License**.

**Permitted**: Reading, learning, research, academic citation, collaboration via PR, developing your own ideas (with attribution).

**Prohibited**: Commercial use without written permission, claiming core concepts as original, removing copyright notices, filing conflicting patents.

**Patent Reserved**: Core concepts including ToneSoul architecture (MGGI, STREI, TSR), Time-Island Protocol, YSTM, Tone Schema, and ΔΣ mechanism.

**Looking for Collaborators**: We welcome researchers and developers interested in AI governance, auditable AI systems, and linguistic responsibility residue.

